  'cprofil.ratesBanner': { it: 'Fissi <strong>liberamente la tua tariffa oraria</strong> nella valuta del tuo paese (<strong>{sym}</strong>), con l\'equivalente in <strong>€</strong> visualizzato. <strong>Nessun minimo imposto</strong> — adatta la tariffa a ogni budget. Fattura mensile = tariffa × impegno (12/16 h); ricevi l\'<strong>80%</strong>. Tariffe <strong>visibili ai genitori</strong>.', tr: '<strong>Saatlik ücretinizi serbestçe</strong>, ülkenizin para biriminde (<strong>{sym}</strong>) belirlersiniz; <strong>€</strong> karşılığı gösterilir. <strong>Asgari sınır yok</strong> — ücreti her bütçeye uyarlayın. Aylık fatura = ücret × taahhüt (12/16 saat); <strong>%80</strong> alırsınız. Ücretler <strong>velilere görünür</strong>.', wo: 'Yaw yaay tànn <strong>sa njëg ci waxtu</strong> ci xaalisu sa réew (<strong>{sym}</strong>), te li mu tollu ci <strong>€</strong> dina feeñ. <strong>Amul njëg gu ndaw gu ñu la teg</strong>. Fakture weer wi = njëg × kóllëre (12/16 waxtu); dangay jot <strong>80%</strong>. Njëg yi, <strong>waajur yi dañu leen di gis</strong>.', sw: 'Unapanga <strong>kwa uhuru bei yako kwa saa</strong> kwa sarafu ya nchi yako (<strong>{sym}</strong>), na thamani kwa <strong>€</strong> inaonyeshwa. <strong>Hakuna kiwango cha chini</strong> — rekebisha bei kwa kila bajeti. Ankara ya mwezi = bei × ahadi (saa 12/16); unapokea <strong>80%</strong>. Bei <strong>zinaonekana kwa wazazi</strong>.' },
